graph TB
    subgraph LLP["llm-d-latency-predictor"]
        direction TB

        subgraph TrainingServer["Training Server (8000/TCP)"]
            TrainAPI["FastAPI REST API<br/>Python/uvicorn"]
            DataBuckets["Stratified Data Buckets<br/>3D: queue × KV cache × prefix cache"]
            Trainer["Background Retrainer<br/>Interval: 1800s"]
            ModelStore["Model Store<br/>/tmp/models/*.joblib"]

            TrainAPI -->|ingests samples| DataBuckets
            DataBuckets -->|stratified data| Trainer
            Trainer -->|serializes via joblib| ModelStore
        end

        subgraph PredictionServer["Prediction Server (8001/TCP)"]
            PredAPI["FastAPI REST API<br/>Python/uvicorn (8 workers)"]
            ModelSyncer["ModelSyncer Thread<br/>Interval: 10s"]
            InMemoryModels["In-Memory Models<br/>XGBoost / LightGBM / BayesianRidge"]
            LocalModels["Local Model Cache<br/>/local_models/*.joblib"]

            ModelSyncer -->|downloads via HTTP| LocalModels
            LocalModels -->|joblib.load + MD5 check| InMemoryModels
            PredAPI -->|inference| InMemoryModels
        end
    end

    %% External actors
    MetricsPipeline["llm-d Metrics Pipeline"] -->|POST /add_training_data_bulk<br/>Latency observations| TrainAPI
    ModelSyncer -->|GET /model/{name}/download<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP| ModelStore

    Gateway["llm-d Gateway<br/>(gateway-api-inference-extension)"] -->|POST /predict/bulk/strict<br/>HTTP 8001/TCP| PredAPI
    PredAPI -->|TTFT + TPOT predictions| Gateway

    K8s["Kubernetes"] -->|GET /healthz, /readyz<br/>Liveness & Readiness probes| TrainAPI
    K8s -->|GET /healthz, /readyz<br/>Liveness & Readiness probes| PredAPI

    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|GET /metrics<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP| TrainAPI

